data.description: Amazing Rancher in Woodcreek Community of Fallbrook. No Mello Roos Taxes, Low HOA.  Newer Hardwood floors, Upgraded Windows, bright and open floor plan with views to rear trees to private gated sanctuary Patio with Large Shade tree and high Privacy fencing. The fully upgraded kitchen features fresh white cabinets, large view window, included Stainless steel Appliances: Refrigerator, Dishwasher, Range, Microwave built-in.  Room for eat in Kitchen or step out to Patio dining. The Vaulted ceiling Brick Fireplace in living room flows to serene views northwest patio and expand entertainment to formal dining room.  Newer Air Condition Unit and Water Heater.  Fully finished Garage with Spacious Attic and Laundry Niche. Orange Fruit Tree Front left.
